nager.php#L708), in a form of https://www.yiiframework.com/doc/api/2.0/yii-db-queryinterface#where()-detail\r\n\r\nThe default implemetation has nothing wrong with it, but i just need to add extra constraints.\r\nIn my case, i need to share rbac info between multiple apps, so having a particular rbac assignment would work in only one of the systems but not all.\r\n### What do you get instead?\r\nExtension of class and overwriting methods used for querying rbac data (in this case assignments) from database. And [some methods](https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/blob/master/framework/rbac/DbManager.php#L1050) are private for DbManager\r\n\r\n### Additional info\r\n\r\n| Q                | A\r\n| ---------------- | ---\r\n| Yii version      | 2.0.25\r\n| PHP version      | 7.3.8-1+ubuntu18.04.1+deb.sury.org+1\r\n| Operating system | Linux  4.15.0-58-generic Ubuntu SMP Tue Aug 6 11:12:41 UTC 2019 x86_64 \r\n","closed_by":{"login":"samdark","id":47294,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ3Mjk0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/47294?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark","html_url":"https://github.com/samdark","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/samdark/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/17522/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"